text.textPath: Engineer of the 1st category, 4+ years old: Linux
(RedOS/Fedora/Astra/CentOS/ALT), virtualization, scripts,
network.
I am an IT specialist, I make practical instructions and
cheat sheets on Linux administration.
The repositories contain step—by-step guides on RedOS,
Fedora, Astra, CentOS and ALT, as well as Linux and
Windows domain interaction.
I collect useful scenario in Scripts, and in
My_ideal_software_IT-environment I fix the optimal set of
tools for the IT infrastructure.
I am also certified in:
• CCNA Security;
• CCNA Routing and Switching: Routing and Switching Essentials;
• CCNA Routing and Switching: Introduction to Networks;
• I am also an expert in evaluating demonstration exams in Network
and System Administration;
• Certified specialist of the Russian operating system Linux RedOS;
• Certified specialist in the course Administration and
diagnostics TATLIN.UNIFIED GEN2;

of TATLIN.UNIFIED GEN2;
